1
01:00:00,000 --> 01:00:01,599
<b>This is a law that stripped French</b>

2
01:00:01,599 --> 01:00:04,166
<b>citizens of their jobs, their rights and</b>

3
01:00:04,166 --> 01:00:06,733
<b>their place in public life, based on</b>

4
01:00:06,733 --> 01:00:07,833
<b>their grandparents' race.</b>

5
01:00:08,699 --> 01:00:10,866
<b>It was written in French and if you don't</b>

6
01:00:10,866 --> 01:00:11,900
<b>read French you've</b>

7
01:00:11,900 --> 01:00:13,166
<b>probably never read it.</b>

8
01:00:13,633 --> 01:00:15,199
<b>The United States Holocaust Memorial</b>

9
01:00:15,199 --> 01:00:17,166
<b>Museum describes its provisions.</b>

10
01:00:17,766 --> 01:00:19,266
<b>Yad Vashem summarizes them.</b>

11
01:00:19,933 --> 01:00:22,133
<b>Academic books quote sections of it.</b>

12
01:00:22,400 --> 01:00:24,633
<b>But a readable, clause-by-clause English</b>

13
01:00:24,633 --> 01:00:26,133
<b>translation of the full text?</b>

14
01:00:26,733 --> 01:00:29,266
<b>I couldn't find one, so I made one.</b>

15
01:00:29,633 --> 01:00:30,833
<b>And then there's something else.</b>

16
01:00:31,266 --> 01:00:33,433
<b>A draft of this law, covered in</b>

17
01:00:33,433 --> 01:00:35,133
<b>handwritten annotations from the French</b>

18
01:00:35,133 --> 01:00:36,266
<b>head of state himself.</b>

19
01:00:37,099 --> 01:00:38,566
<b>Those annotations have never been</b>

20
01:00:38,566 --> 01:00:41,066
<b>translated or walked through in English.</b>

21
01:00:42,066 --> 01:00:44,333
<b>They proved he didn't just sign this law.</b>

22
01:00:44,866 --> 01:00:46,866
<b>He personally made it worse.</b>

23
01:00:47,500 --> 01:00:50,133
<b>They proved, but was not the hero that</b>

24
01:00:50,133 --> 01:00:51,566
<b>most people make him out to be.</b>

25
01:00:51,866 --> 01:00:53,000
<b>I'm going to show you both.</b>

26
01:00:53,666 --> 01:00:56,566
<b>On October 3rd, 1940, the Vichy</b>

27
01:00:56,566 --> 01:00:59,266
<b>government published the Statute des</b>

28
01:00:59,266 --> 01:01:01,166
<b>Juifs, the Jewish Statute.</b>

29
01:01:01,733 --> 01:01:03,233
<b>It created a racial</b>

30
01:01:03,233 --> 01:01:05,266
<b>definition of who counted as Jewish.</b>

31
01:01:05,900 --> 01:01:08,566
<b>It banned Jews from almost every position</b>

32
01:01:08,566 --> 01:01:09,699
<b>of public influence.</b>

33
01:01:10,466 --> 01:01:12,199
<b>And it applied those bans across the</b>

34
01:01:12,199 --> 01:01:13,466
<b>entire French Empire.</b>

35
01:01:14,033 --> 01:01:15,933
<b>For decades the official French position</b>

36
01:01:15,933 --> 01:01:17,833
<b>was that Germany imposed this.</b>

37
01:01:18,566 --> 01:01:20,900
<b>After the war, Vichy's own justice</b>

38
01:01:20,900 --> 01:01:22,566
<b>minister, a man named</b>

39
01:01:22,566 --> 01:01:25,500
<b>Joseph Barthélemy, said, and this</b>

40
01:01:25,500 --> 01:01:28,233
<b>is a direct quote, "This legislation is</b>

41
01:01:28,233 --> 01:01:29,466
<b>not a French initiative.</b>

42
01:01:29,833 --> 01:01:31,633
<b>It is entirely of German origin."</b>

43
01:01:32,733 --> 01:01:34,766
<b>The archives proved that was a lie.</b>

44
01:01:35,599 --> 01:01:37,533
<b>We know this because of three things.</b>

45
01:01:38,266 --> 01:01:40,566
<b>First, the armistice France signed with</b>

46
01:01:40,566 --> 01:01:42,400
<b>Germany in June 1940</b>

47
01:01:42,400 --> 01:01:44,133
<b>said nothing about Jews.</b>

48
01:01:45,599 --> 01:01:47,733
<b>Historians Marrus and Paxton went through</b>

49
01:01:47,733 --> 01:01:49,666
<b>both the German and French archives.</b>

50
01:01:50,433 --> 01:01:53,133
<b>Their conclusion, close study of German</b>

51
01:01:53,133 --> 01:01:54,366
<b>and French archives,</b>

52
01:01:54,833 --> 01:01:56,433
<b>reveals no German demand</b>

53
01:01:56,433 --> 01:01:58,533
<b>in 1940 that Vichy</b>

54
01:01:58,533 --> 01:02:00,699
<b>adopt an anti-Jewish policy.</b>

55
01:02:01,466 --> 01:02:03,833
<b>Second, France was already passing</b>

56
01:02:03,833 --> 01:02:05,133
<b>anti-Jewish measures</b>

57
01:02:05,133 --> 01:02:06,833
<b>before Germany issued anything.</b>

58
01:02:07,366 --> 01:02:09,933
<b>In July 1940, they restricted public</b>

59
01:02:09,933 --> 01:02:11,333
<b>service jobs to people</b>

60
01:02:11,333 --> 01:02:12,533
<b>born of French fathers.</b>

61
01:02:13,733 --> 01:02:14,733
<b>In August, they</b>

62
01:02:14,733 --> 01:02:16,233
<b>restricted the medical profession.</b>

63
01:02:16,833 --> 01:02:19,000
<b>In late August, they repealed the</b>

64
01:02:19,000 --> 01:02:21,333
<b>Marchandeau law, the law that had made</b>

65
01:02:21,333 --> 01:02:22,433
<b>anti-Semitic attacks</b>

66
01:02:22,433 --> 01:02:23,599
<b>in the press illegal.</b>

67
01:02:24,099 --> 01:02:25,433
<b>All of this before any</b>

68
01:02:25,433 --> 01:02:26,766
<b>German ordinance on Jews.</b>

69
01:02:27,666 --> 01:02:30,400
<b>And thirdly, when Germany finally did act</b>

70
01:02:30,400 --> 01:02:32,066
<b>on September 27,</b>

71
01:02:32,766 --> 01:02:34,833
<b>1940, what they did demand</b>

72
01:02:35,033 --> 01:02:35,733
<b>was limited.</b>

73
01:02:36,233 --> 01:02:39,033
<b>A census and property registration, only</b>

74
01:02:39,033 --> 01:02:40,266
<b>in the occupied zone.</b>

75
01:02:41,000 --> 01:02:41,866
<b>And they used a religious</b>

76
01:02:41,866 --> 01:02:43,466
<b>definition of who was Jewish.</b>

77
01:02:44,533 --> 01:02:46,566
<b>Six days later, France responded with</b>

78
01:02:46,566 --> 01:02:48,933
<b>something far broader, a racial</b>

79
01:02:48,933 --> 01:02:51,033
<b>definition, a full professional</b>

80
01:02:51,199 --> 01:02:53,133
<b>purge applied across</b>

81
01:02:53,133 --> 01:02:54,566
<b>the entire French empire.</b>

82
01:02:56,000 --> 01:02:57,333
<b>France didn't just follow Germany.</b>

83
01:02:58,433 --> 01:02:59,166
<b>France went further.</b>

84
01:02:59,833 --> 01:03:00,666
<b>The first thing the law</b>

85
01:03:00,666 --> 01:03:02,433
<b>does is define its target.</b>

86
01:03:03,166 --> 01:03:05,000
<b>And the word it uses is</b>

87
01:03:05,000 --> 01:03:06,966
<b>"race", not "religion".</b>

88
01:03:07,566 --> 01:03:09,733
<b>"Race juive", the Jewish race.</b>

89
01:03:10,533 --> 01:03:12,533
<b>If you had three Jewish grandparents, you</b>

90
01:03:12,533 --> 01:03:13,599
<b>were counted as a Jew.</b>

91
01:03:14,599 --> 01:03:15,466
<b>It didn't matter if you</b>

92
01:03:15,466 --> 01:03:16,533
<b>were baptized Catholic.</b>

93
01:03:17,166 --> 01:03:18,233
<b>It didn't matter if you'd</b>

94
01:03:18,233 --> 01:03:19,633
<b>never set foot in a synagogue.</b>

95
01:03:20,233 --> 01:03:22,166
<b>If you had two Jewish grandparents, you</b>

96
01:03:22,166 --> 01:03:23,400
<b>could escape the definition.</b>

97
01:03:24,133 --> 01:03:27,133
<b>Unless your spouse was Jewish, then you</b>

98
01:03:27,133 --> 01:03:28,800
<b>were fully Jewish under the law.</b>

99
01:03:29,866 --> 01:03:32,699
<b>And notice, the law never defines what</b>

100
01:03:32,699 --> 01:03:34,233
<b>makes a grandparent Jewish.</b>

101
01:03:34,699 --> 01:03:35,933
<b>The definition is circular.</b>

102
01:03:36,766 --> 01:03:38,066
<b>That's not sloppy drafting.</b>

103
01:03:38,566 --> 01:03:40,099
<b>A vague definition gave</b>

104
01:03:40,099 --> 01:03:41,866
<b>authorities maximum discretion.</b>

105
01:03:43,266 --> 01:03:44,666
<b>Marrus and Paxton again.</b>

106
01:03:45,466 --> 01:03:47,933
<b>Vichy's "Statut des juifs" went further than</b>

107
01:03:47,933 --> 01:03:48,866
<b>the German ordinance.</b>

108
01:03:49,533 --> 01:03:51,533
<b>Whereas the German ordinance spoke only</b>

109
01:03:51,533 --> 01:03:53,166
<b>of religion, the Vichy</b>

110
01:03:53,166 --> 01:03:54,933
<b>law spoke openly of race.</b>

111
01:03:56,366 --> 01:03:57,733
<b>Article 2 is the ban list.</b>

112
01:03:58,366 --> 01:03:59,300
<b>And when you read it,</b>

113
01:03:59,533 --> 01:04:00,733
<b>you understand the scale.</b>

114
01:04:01,300 --> 01:04:03,400
<b>Jews were banned from head of state,</b>

115
01:04:03,766 --> 01:04:05,133
<b>every court from the</b>

116
01:04:05,133 --> 01:04:06,500
<b>Supreme Court down to the local</b>

117
01:04:06,633 --> 01:04:09,933
<b>magistrate, every elected assembly, all</b>

118
01:04:09,933 --> 01:04:12,966
<b>prefects, all police, all</b>

119
01:04:12,966 --> 01:04:15,466
<b>diplomats, all colonial governors,</b>

120
01:04:16,266 --> 01:04:19,966
<b>all military officers, all teachers, any</b>

121
01:04:19,966 --> 01:04:20,900
<b>director of a company</b>

122
01:04:20,900 --> 01:04:22,233
<b>receiving public money.</b>

123
01:04:23,066 --> 01:04:23,966
<b>That's not a ban on a</b>

124
01:04:23,966 --> 01:04:25,333
<b>few senior positions.</b>

125
01:04:25,733 --> 01:04:27,666
<b>That's a systematic removal from every</b>

126
01:04:27,666 --> 01:04:28,866
<b>institution that exercises</b>

127
01:04:28,866 --> 01:04:31,099
<b>authority, shapes culture or</b>

128
01:04:31,099 --> 01:04:32,033
<b>controls information.</b>

129
01:04:33,233 --> 01:04:37,099
<b>By 1942, roughly 3,400 public servants</b>

130
01:04:37,099 --> 01:04:38,933
<b>had been dismissed in mainland France,</b>

131
01:04:39,533 --> 01:04:41,599
<b>another 2,500 in Algeria.</b>

132
01:04:42,400 --> 01:04:45,733
<b>Article 5 bans Jews without condition or</b>

133
01:04:45,733 --> 01:04:48,966
<b>reservation, from directing, managing or</b>

134
01:04:48,966 --> 01:04:50,366
<b>editing any newspaper,</b>

135
01:04:51,066 --> 01:04:52,666
<b>magazine or periodical.</b>

136
01:04:53,533 --> 01:04:56,099
<b>Then cinema, directors, producers,</b>

137
01:04:56,666 --> 01:04:58,666
<b>screenwriters, then radio.</b>

138
01:04:59,333 --> 01:05:00,500
<b>No war hero exceptions.</b>

139
01:05:01,466 --> 01:05:02,699
<b>No exemptions at all.</b>

140
01:05:03,233 --> 01:05:05,033
<b>The only thing Jews could still publish</b>

141
01:05:05,033 --> 01:05:06,366
<b>was scientific journals.</b>

142
01:05:07,833 --> 01:05:09,533
<b>That one exception tells you everything</b>

143
01:05:09,533 --> 01:05:10,866
<b>about the law's purpose.</b>

144
01:05:11,766 --> 01:05:13,699
<b>A Jewish journalist isn't banned because</b>

145
01:05:13,699 --> 01:05:14,866
<b>they're bad at their job.</b>

146
01:05:15,666 --> 01:05:17,566
<b>They're banned because they shape what</b>

147
01:05:17,566 --> 01:05:18,633
<b>French people think.</b>

148
01:05:19,366 --> 01:05:21,266
<b>This is about controlling who tells</b>

149
01:05:21,266 --> 01:05:22,333
<b>France its stories.</b>

150
01:05:23,500 --> 01:05:25,633
<b>With one sentence, they extended the law</b>

151
01:05:25,633 --> 01:05:27,233
<b>across the entire French empire.</b>

152
01:05:28,099 --> 01:05:31,533
<b>In Morocco, 32 of 37 Jewish lawyers were</b>

153
01:05:31,533 --> 01:05:32,466
<b>removed from the bar.</b>

154
01:05:33,266 --> 01:05:35,699
<b>Four days after this statute, a separate</b>

155
01:05:35,699 --> 01:05:36,533
<b>law stripped over</b>

156
01:05:36,533 --> 01:05:39,233
<b>100,000 Algerian Jews of the</b>

157
01:05:39,233 --> 01:05:41,400
<b>citizenship they'd held for 70 years.</b>

158
01:05:42,466 --> 01:05:44,233
<b>But it didn't stop in North Africa.</b>

159
01:05:44,900 --> 01:05:46,666
<b>French administrators applied this law</b>

160
01:05:46,666 --> 01:05:49,033
<b>everywhere, including territories</b>

161
01:05:49,033 --> 01:05:50,400
<b>thousands of miles from</b>

162
01:05:50,400 --> 01:05:51,733
<b>the nearest German soldier.</b>

163
01:05:52,133 --> 01:05:53,266
<b>In French Indochina,</b>

164
01:05:53,566 --> 01:05:55,199
<b>they counted 140 Jews.</b>

165
01:05:56,133 --> 01:05:58,066
<b>French West Africa, 110.</b>

166
01:05:58,666 --> 01:05:59,966
<b>Martinique, 36.</b>

167
01:06:00,633 --> 01:06:01,766
<b>Guadeloupe, 22.</b>

168
01:06:02,366 --> 01:06:03,666
<b>Madagascar, 26.</b>

169
01:06:04,333 --> 01:06:06,433
<b>There was no military requirement to</b>

170
01:06:06,433 --> 01:06:08,466
<b>register 22 people in Guadeloupe.</b>

171
01:06:09,033 --> 01:06:09,766
<b>There were no German</b>

172
01:06:09,766 --> 01:06:11,099
<b>troops in Martinique.</b>

173
01:06:11,933 --> 01:06:13,099
<b>This wasn't geopolitics.</b>

174
01:06:13,466 --> 01:06:15,300
<b>This was administrative zeal.</b>

175
01:06:16,366 --> 01:06:18,066
<b>Marrus and Paxton call this the</b>

176
01:06:18,066 --> 01:06:19,866
<b>definitive proof that Vichy's</b>

177
01:06:19,866 --> 01:06:21,366
<b>antisemitism was indigenous.</b>

178
01:06:23,066 --> 01:06:23,699
<b>That's the law.</b>

179
01:06:24,300 --> 01:06:25,666
<b>Now I want to show you something that was</b>

180
01:06:25,666 --> 01:06:27,133
<b>hidden for 70 years.</b>

181
01:06:28,133 --> 01:06:31,400
<b>In 2010, 70 years to the day after the</b>

182
01:06:31,400 --> 01:06:33,066
<b>statute was signed, a</b>

183
01:06:33,066 --> 01:06:34,966
<b>lawyer, a Nazi hunter named</b>

184
01:06:35,033 --> 01:06:37,966
<b>Serge Klarsfeld, held a press conference</b>

185
01:06:37,966 --> 01:06:40,699
<b>at the Memorial de la Shoah in Paris.</b>

186
01:06:41,133 --> 01:06:43,166
<b>He had a typed draft of the statute,</b>

187
01:06:43,766 --> 01:06:45,433
<b>stamped "DOCUMENT</b>

188
01:06:45,433 --> 01:06:47,800
<b>CONFIDENTIEL", covered in handwritten</b>

189
01:06:47,966 --> 01:06:48,666
<b>annotations.</b>

190
01:06:49,933 --> 01:06:51,766
<b>Handwriting experts confirmed they</b>

191
01:06:51,766 --> 01:06:52,266
<b>were Philippe</b>

192
01:06:52,266 --> 01:06:54,199
<b>Pétain's, the head of the Vichy</b>

193
01:06:54,566 --> 01:06:54,633
<b>state.</b>

194
01:06:55,766 --> 01:06:56,733
<b>I have this document.</b>

195
01:06:57,333 --> 01:06:58,933
<b>I have translated his notes.</b>

196
01:06:59,933 --> 01:07:02,066
<b>The typed draft listed specific</b>

197
01:07:02,066 --> 01:07:03,433
<b>educational administrators,</b>

198
01:07:04,366 --> 01:07:06,366
<b>directors, inspectors, school</b>

199
01:07:06,800 --> 01:07:06,900
<b>directors.</b>

200
01:07:08,033 --> 01:07:10,733
<b>Pétain wrote in the margin "tout personnel</b>

201
01:07:10,733 --> 01:07:12,666
<b>enseignant", all</b>

202
01:07:12,666 --> 01:07:14,866
<b>teaching personnel, not just</b>

203
01:07:14,866 --> 01:07:17,400
<b>the people who run the schools, every</b>

204
01:07:17,400 --> 01:07:18,866
<b>teacher at every level.</b>

205
01:07:19,533 --> 01:07:20,933
<b>The typed draft banned Jews</b>

206
01:07:20,933 --> 01:07:22,833
<b>from specific named institutions.</b>

207
01:07:23,833 --> 01:07:26,833
<b>Pétain added "toutes assemblées issues</b>

208
01:07:26,833 --> 01:07:29,066
<b>de l'élection" all</b>

209
01:07:29,066 --> 01:07:30,466
<b>assemblies arising from</b>

210
01:07:30,533 --> 01:07:34,133
<b>elections, every municipal council, every</b>

211
01:07:34,133 --> 01:07:35,633
<b>departmental council,</b>

212
01:07:36,333 --> 01:07:37,466
<b>every elected body in</b>

213
01:07:37,466 --> 01:07:38,633
<b>France and its empire.</b>

214
01:07:39,666 --> 01:07:40,766
<b>The draft banned Jews</b>

215
01:07:40,766 --> 01:07:41,833
<b>from the high courts.</b>

216
01:07:42,833 --> 01:07:45,800
<b>Pétain extended it to "justices de paix",</b>

217
01:07:45,800 --> 01:07:48,400
<b>the village magistrate courts, the lowest</b>

218
01:07:48,533 --> 01:07:49,933
<b>level of French justice.</b>

219
01:07:50,633 --> 01:07:51,400
<b>And then there's the</b>

220
01:07:51,400 --> 01:07:52,733
<b>change that matters most.</b>

221
01:07:53,466 --> 01:07:56,666
<b>The typed draft, already harsh, had a</b>

222
01:07:56,666 --> 01:07:57,533
<b>protection clause,</b>

223
01:07:58,099 --> 01:08:00,766
<b>condition A, read "être descendant</b>

224
01:08:00,766 --> 01:08:02,333
<b>de Juifs nés français ou</b>

225
01:08:02,333 --> 01:08:03,433
<b>naturalisés avant</b>

226
01:08:03,433 --> 01:08:05,666
<b>l'année 1860" to</b>

227
01:08:05,666 --> 01:08:08,266
<b>be a descendant of Jews born French or</b>

228
01:08:08,266 --> 01:08:10,366
<b>naturalized before the year 1860.</b>

229
01:08:11,400 --> 01:08:13,333
<b>That's an 80-year grandfather clause.</b>

230
01:08:14,033 --> 01:08:15,933
<b>If your family had been French since</b>

231
01:08:15,933 --> 01:08:18,066
<b>Napoleon III, you were protected.</b>

232
01:08:18,899 --> 01:08:20,800
<b>These were France's most established,</b>

233
01:08:21,300 --> 01:08:23,199
<b>most assimilated Jewish families.</b>

234
01:08:23,866 --> 01:08:24,533
<b>Families who had been</b>

235
01:08:24,533 --> 01:08:25,766
<b>French for generations.</b>

236
01:08:26,600 --> 01:08:27,833
<b>Pétain drew a line</b>

237
01:08:27,833 --> 01:08:29,000
